@startuml sequence_suggestion
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Proactive Suggestion

participant "SuggestionDetector\n(BackgroundService)" as D
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "suggestions" as DB
actor User
participant "HomePage" as UI
participant "GET /api/suggestions" as API

D -> CTX: load last 14d interactions per user
D -> D: apply heuristics
D -> CTX: UPSERT Suggestion (by Key)
CTX -> DB: INSERT/UPDATE

User -> UI: load home
UI -> API: GET /api/suggestions
API -> CTX: active (DismissedAt is null, age<7d)
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> API: row
API --> UI: suggestion
UI --> User: render gradient card

User -> UI: tap Dismiss
UI -> API: POST /api/suggestions/{key}/dismiss
API -> CTX: UPDATE DismissedAt
API --> UI: 204
UI -> UI: hide card

@enduml
